 -- Ricardo Mones <mones@debian.org>  Sat, 23 Dec 2006 20:38:30 +0100

claws-mail (2.7.0~rc1-1) experimental; urgency=low

  * Package renaming, upstream name is now Claws Mail.
  * debian/README.Debian
  - Updated included libraries
  * debian/control, debian/rules
  - Renamed sylpheed-claws-gtk2* to claws-mail*
  - Added claws-mail-tools to include the scripts as sylpheed-claws-scripts
    are no longer valid because of rc dir name change
  * debian/inst-manual.sh, debian/watch
  - Documentation package and upstream tarball names changed
  * patches/01configure.*, patches/02ml_menu_fix.*, patches/00list
  - Removed obsolete patches, updated list
  * debian/rules, debian/control
  - rename symlink and set claws-mail to replace sylpheed-claws-gtk2

