sylpheed-claws-gtk2 (1.9.13-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release. First for unstable.
  * Rebuilt with newer libaspell (Closes: #318889)
  * debian/control, patches/00configure.patch
  - Added new Norwegian Bokmal translation.
  * debian/rules
  - Added pgpcore.so to the pgpmime deb, fixed icon names.
  * debian/control, debian/rules
  - Added new pgpinline plugin, now in upstream source tree.
  * debian/README.Debian
  - Updated and rationale for not having a new ppgcore package.
  * 10get_xface_from_file.patch, 11mark_trashed_as_read.patch
  - Added feature patches.
  * debian/sylpheed-claws-gtk2.desktop
  - Added [es] comment.
  * debian/docs
  - Fixed, added RELEASE_NOTES.claws.
  * debian/control, debian/copyright
  - Fixed package description, copyright and Debian policy version.
  * 90fix-pt_BR-view.menu.patch
  - Temporary fix (segfault clicking View menu on pt_BR locale).

